# Project specific
# Harness runtime artifacts (StatusManager .cdh-run-*.status etc.)
# These belong *only* inside --target-dir (e.g. /tmp/some-target/).
# Never commit them to the source repo, even if a launch wrote them to cwd.
# The *.status was present since initial commit but made explicit here
# to prevent any confusion about temporary run artifacts from /tmp or launches.
.cdh-run-*.status
.cdh-run-*.status.last-crash
*.cdh-*
*.status
state/
outputs/
patches/
*.log
